<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Data Deletion – {{appName}}</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; color: #1a1a2e; line-height: 1.7; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 2rem; color: #3730a3; }
    p, li { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #374151; }
    ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    a { color: #4f46e5; }
    .meta { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .steps { background: #f5f3ff; border-left: 4px solid #6d28d9; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
    .steps ol { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Data Deletion Request</h1>
  <p class="meta">Application: <strong>{{appName}}</strong> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Last updated: {{lastUpdated}}</p>

  <p>We respect your right to control your personal data. This page explains how to request the deletion of your data associated with <strong>{{appName}}</strong>.</p>

  <h2>What Data Will Be Deleted</h2>
  {{#if hasCollectedData}}
  <p>Upon a verified deletion request, we will permanently remove the following data types associated with your account or device:</p>
  <ul>
    {{#each collectedData}}
    <li>{{this.label}}</li>
    {{/each}}
  </ul>
  {{else}}
  <p>This app does not store personal data on our servers. Any locally stored preferences can be cleared by uninstalling the app.</p>
  {{/if}}

  {{#if hasUserAccounts}}
  <h2>How to Delete Your Account</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <ol>
      <li>Open the <strong>{{appName}}</strong> app on your device.</li>
      <li>Navigate to <strong>Settings → Account</strong>.</li>
      <li>Tap <strong>Delete Account</strong> and confirm your choice.</li>
      <li>Your account and associated data will be permanently deleted within 30 days.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  <h2>Request Deletion via Email</h2>
  <p>If you are unable to delete your data through the app, you may submit a deletion request by emailing us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a> with the subject line <strong>"Data Deletion Request – {{appName}}"</strong>.</p>
  <p>Please include the following in your email:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your name (or username / user ID if applicable)</li>
    <li>The email address associated with your account</li>
    <li>A brief description of the data you want deleted</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Processing Time</h2>
  <p>We will process your request within <strong>30 days</strong> of verification and send a confirmation to your email address.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For questions about data deletion, contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>
